text: Menn Krecke (20 December 1922 - 29 July 1976) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1922 births Category:1976 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Luxembourg City
